&nbsp; Click To Open Mpumalanga ANC Top Five held a meeting at the &#8220;residence of the chairperson&#8221; on 7 December 2008. Some interesting decisions were taken, including the decision that Jimmy Mohlala must be removed as the Speaker of the Mbombela Local Municipality. Mohlala declined and made a successful submission to the ANC head office Luthuli House, and an instruction from LuthuliHouse was the he stays put. A month later he was killed.